cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about data augmentation for deep learning models in image classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the impact of data augmentation on the generalization performance of deep learning models, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper uses deep learning models, which can be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper focuses on image classification, which is a sub-topic of cs.MM (Multimedia).
